name: Expat Greece ASE UCITS ETF
description_en: The Expat Greece ASE UCITS ETF seeks to track the FTSE ATHEX Composite index. The FTSE ATHEX Composite index tracks the 60 largest companies from Greece. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 1.38% p.a.. The Expat Greece ASE UCITS ETF is the only ETF that tracks the FTSE ATHEX Composite index. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by sampling technique (buying a selection of the most relevant index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The Expat Greece ASE UCITS ETF is a very small ETF with 0m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 21 December 2017 and is domiciled in Bulgaria. Show more Show less
description_cs: Expat Řecko ASE UCITS ETF se snaží sledovat kompozitní index FTSE Athex.Index FTSE Athex Composite sleduje 60 největších společností z Řecka.TER (celkový poměr nákladů) činí 1,38% p.a. Expat Řecko ASE UCITS ETF je jediný ETF, který sleduje kompozitní index FTSE Athex.ETF replikuje výkon základního indexu technikou vzorkování (nákup výběru nejdůležitějších složek indexu).dividenday v ETF jsou akumulovány a reinvestovány do ETF.Expat Řecko ASE UCITS ETF je velmi malá ETF s managementem 0m euro.ETF byl spuštěn 21. prosince 2017 a je se sídlem v Bulharsku.Ukázat více show méně

name: Expat Hungary BUX UCITS ETF
description_en: The Expat Hungary BUX UCITS ETF seeks to track the BUX index. The BUX index tracks the main Hungarian companies. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 1.38% p.a.. The Expat Hungary BUX UCITS ETF is the only ETF that tracks the BUX index. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by full replication (buying all the index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The Expat Hungary BUX UCITS ETF is a very small ETF with 0m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 5 February 2018 and is domiciled in Bulgaria. Show more Show less
